pycurator.collectors.term_type_collectors.FigshareCollector

pycurator.collectors.term_type_collectors.FigshareCollector#

class pycurator.collectors.term_type_collectors.FigshareCollector(search_terms: Optional[collections.abc.Collection[pycurator._typing.SearchTerm]] = None, search_types: Optional[collections.abc.Collection[pycurator._typing.SearchType]] = None, credentials: Optional[str] = None)#

Figshare collector for search term and type queries.

Parameters

  • search_terms (list-like, optional (default=None)) – Terms to search over. Can be (re)set via set_search_terms() or passed in directly to search functions.

  • search_types (list-like, optional (default=None)) – Data types to search over. Can be (re)set via set_search_types() or passed in directly to search functions to override set parameter.

  • credentials (str, optional (default=None)) – JSON filepath containing credentials in form {repository_name}: {key}.
